{"tid":342003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係越黎越頂唔撚順港鐵","createTime":"2017-07-31T09:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T15:32:59.000Z","uid":87388,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f862b7419a6bee56fd3362675355352a7ec8e303","tid":342003,"uid":87388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:14:03.000Z","msg":"本身已經好撚多人 之後又多左成堆強國狗搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講野又大聲又陏黎陏去唔知做乜勁<br />\n個月台又熱撚到仆街 仲要貴<br />\n有巴士一定唔搭地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc8207c8a91b84148680795274fbe9822013ed3","tid":342003,"uid":100016,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:15:42.000Z","msg":"少你一個搭會執咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253a171d8211a0f3252b7a6b201eae2b3ba7261d","tid":342003,"uid":30837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:16:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>少你一個搭會執咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0145048c2ca40448624031e410b71fbab6878a60","tid":342003,"uid":87388,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:17:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>少你一個搭會執咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔搭係為自己爽<br />\n唔係想佢執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40de439aa54084ae94ea570ec51898959c77ed3d","tid":342003,"uid":5077,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:19:53.000Z","msg":"班大陸閪真係痴撚線，成日痴身痴世，<br />\n明明有位都要痴埋嚟手臂掂手臂先安落，<br />\n明明無位又要間硬企埋嚟搏人讓位甚至讓撚埋個扶手俾佢地，<br />\n啲細路又喺到跑嚟跑去，<br />\n一係就喺個位到企吓跳吓，<br />\n屌呢個乜撚嘢國家嚟㗎"},{"pid":"d934c043f60a2250b3c7662c3256eb63e2e06772","tid":342003,"uid":87388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:23:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班大陸閪真係痴撚線，成日痴身痴世，<br />\n明明有位都要痴埋嚟手臂掂手臂先安落，<br />\n明明無位又要間硬企埋嚟搏人讓位甚至讓撚埋個扶手俾佢地，<br />\n啲細路又喺到跑嚟跑去，<br />\n一係就喺個位到企吓跳吓，<br />\n屌呢個乜撚嘢國家嚟㗎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD細路最煩 又大聲又走黎走去<br />\n當正遊樂場咁玩<br />\n你啤佢一下佢又喊曬口咁番去搵老母<br />\n強國人既教育真係好成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f672c59355d2483979e5fd9d71d9ad9958ebad9","tid":342003,"uid":22974,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:26:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cea1e6600fe3344e14cae95a684b1c6e36df87d3","tid":342003,"uid":1274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:31:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班大陸閪真係痴撚線，成日痴身痴世，<br />\n明明有位都要痴埋嚟手臂掂手臂先安落，<br />\n明明無位又要間硬企埋嚟搏人讓位甚至讓撚埋個扶手俾佢地，<br />\n啲細路又喺到跑嚟跑去，<br />\n一係就喺個位到企吓跳吓，<br />\n屌呢個乜撚嘢國家嚟㗎</blockquote><br />\n你形容得非常到位，不過未講全面，<br />\n仲有臭未講，唔明點解啲人可以咁臭，成陣鐵銹味定黃泥味咁，真喺閉氣都閉死"},{"pid":"a28c2d698f5dfe2098a343950222dd784c4dde53","tid":342003,"uid":87388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:32:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己搵得少就話港鐵貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁叻去買benz渣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對比其他國家港鐵係平既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係窮撚日日出入計番筆交通費出黎都係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72cc53cddc31dca8707356053e2af8f48282e50a","tid":342003,"uid":62830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:35:28.000Z","msg":"呢排啲死肥佬臭到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c440cb932c7d628fce5606c6b61636373722868e","tid":342003,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:37:12.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n好撚嘈<br />\n低等種族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b209ac2c388f0f7c819b84d7480ab444282abab","tid":342003,"uid":17197,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:40:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己搵得少就話港鐵貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁叻去買benz渣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對比其他國家港鐵係平既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係窮撚日日出入計番筆交通費出黎都係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日日早幾個鐘起身行返工囉小小錢都肉赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce37206e28d38cd7f2f5efa0327376f424d83c89","tid":342003,"uid":87388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:46:20.000Z","msg":"同埋唔知點解月台可以咁焗咁熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明車上面就好好冷氣"},{"pid":"8a05c931a5f55d3705a65683557a7a1081580356","tid":342003,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:24:42.000Z","msg":"得罪講句<br />\n係支那人既問題喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9bee815f0d260819d2d4d118d9a3aade7a5de3d","tid":342003,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋唔知點解月台可以咁焗咁熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明車上面就好好冷氣</blockquote><br />\n深圳化<br />\n<br />\n就係等你快d迫入車箱快d走"},{"pid":"50e3e66dc6c048eb199c6541dc421a72e8e57867","tid":342003,"uid":87388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:37:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同埋唔知點解月台可以咁焗咁熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明車上面就好好冷氣</blockquote><